                         Orkan Software/Old Vikings
                                  present

                                * P A T I *


  This archive contains demoversion of a brand new platform game titled
Pati's Dreams. Pati (Patricia, that is) goes to sleep and she dreams of
several adventures. In this demoversion you can play one of them - Cave
Exploring. There are three more adventures: Toys, Sweets and Forest in the
full version. Each adventure consists of five game levels. Full version
incudes also:
- new sound modules
- new sound FX
- bug fixes
- and many more!

Requirements: AGA, 68020+, 2MB Chip RAM
Installation: Just copy contents of this archive into desired directory.
To run double-click Pati's icon.
If you have only 2MB memory, you will propably have to boot with no
startup-sequence, then cd to Pati's directory and run 'Pati'.


Check Orkan's homepage at: http://www.kki.net.pl/orkans
If you have any suggestion, contact the authors at: kite@rh311.p.lodz.pl

Enjoy!
